Class TermComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin.TermComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<ModelTerm>

    public class TermComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<ModelTerm>
    Orders ModelTerms for user display. The terms are ordered by, in order of precendence:
    1. Type (Constant, then Rules, then Variables)
    2. Display Name
    3. For Discrete Variables, the option index.
